# Структура проекта

```
app/src/main/java/com/dayscounter/
├── data/
│   ├── database/         # Room entities, DAO, DB, converters, mappers
│   ├── provider/         # DaysFormatter, ResourceProvider
│   ├── preferences/      # AppSettingsDataStore
│   └── repository/       # ItemRepositoryImpl
├── domain/
│   ├── exception/        # ItemException
│   ├── model/            # Domain entities
│   ├── repository/       # ItemRepository interface
│   └── usecase/          # Use cases, IconManager, BackupException, BackupItem
├── ui/
│   ├── ds/               # Design System components (reusable)
│   ├── screens/          # Compose screens
│   ├── state/            # UI state classes
│   ├── theme/            # App theme
│   └── viewmodel/        # ViewModels
├── navigation/           # Navigation routes
├── reminder/             # Reminder logic (worker, notification)
├── analytics/            # FirebaseAnalyticsHelper
├── crash/                # CrashlyticsHelper
├── di/                   # AppModule, FormatterModule
├── util/                 # AndroidLogger, AppConstants, Logger, NoOpLogger, ThemeUtils
├── DaysCounterApplication.kt
└── MainActivity.kt
```

## Правила

- Экраны → `ui/screens/`
- Компоненты UI → `ui/ds/`
- ViewModels → `ui/viewmodel/`
- UI State → `ui/state/`
- Тесты → `test/` (unit), `androidTest/` (integration/UI), структура зеркалит код
